</main>
<section class="cta-band" aria-label="Ta kontakt">
  <div class="wrap cta-band-inner reveal">
    <div>
      <h2>Klar for å ta lappen?</h2>
      <p>Det første steget er å ta kontakt – ring, send SMS eller meld deg på i dag.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-band-actions">
      <a class="btn btn-light" href="/pamelding">Meld deg på opplæring</a>
      <a class="btn btn-outline-light" href="/kurs">Sjå kurskalenderen</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="wrap footer-grid">
    <div>
      <h2 class="footer-title">Kontakt</h2>
      <address>
        <strong><%= settings.siteName %></strong><br>
        <%= settings.address.street %><br>
        <%= settings.address.zip %> <%= settings.address.city %>
      </address>
      <p><a href="mailto:<%= settings.email %>"><%= settings.email %></a></p>
      <% if (settings.orgnr) { %><p class="muted">Org.nr. <%= settings.orgnr %></p><% } %>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2 class="footer-title">Avdelingar</h2>
      <ul class="footer-list">
        <% settings.locations.forEach(function(l) { %>
          <li>
            <strong><%= l.name %></strong>
            <% if (l.person) { %><span class="muted"><%= l.person %></span><% } %>
            <a class="footer-phone" href="tel:+47<%= String(l.phone).replace(/\s/g,'') %>"><%= l.phone %></a>
          </li>
        <% }) %>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2 class="footer-title">Opningstider</h2>
      <ul class="footer-list">
        <% (settings.hours || []).forEach(function(h) { %>
          <li><strong><%= h.label %></strong> <span><%= h.value %></span></li>
        <% }) %>
      </ul>
      <div class="footer-social">
        <% if (settings.social.facebook) { %>
          <a href="<%= settings.social.facebook %>" rel="noopener" target="_blank" aria-label="Nordfjord Trafikk på Facebook">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path fill="currentColor" d="M13.5 21v-7h2.4l.4-3h-2.8V9.1c0-.9.3-1.5 1.6-1.5h1.3V4.9c-.2 0-1-.1-2-.1-2 0-3.4 1.2-3.4 3.5V11H8.6v3H11v7Z"/></svg>
          </a>
        <% } %>
        <% if (settings.social.instagram) { %>
          <a href="<%= settings.social.instagram %>" rel="noopener" target="_blank" aria-label="Nordfjord Trafikk på Instagram">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path fill="currentColor" d="M12 8.8A3.2 3.2 0 1 0 12 15.2 3.2 3.2 0 0 0 12 8.8Zm0-2.1a5.3 5.3 0 1 1 0 10.6 5.3 5.3 0 0 1 0-10.6Zm6.8-.3a1.3 1.3 0 1 1-2.6 0 1.3 1.3 0 0 1 2.6 0ZM12 4.6c-2.4 0-2.7 0-3.7.1-.9 0-1.5.2-2 .4-.5.2-.9.5-1.2.8-.4.4-.6.7-.8 1.2-.2.5-.4 1-.4 2-.1 1-.1 1.3-.1 3.9s0 2.9.1 3.9c0 .9.2 1.5.4 2 .2.5.5.9.8 1.2.4.4.7.6 1.2.8.5.2 1 .4 2 .4 1 .1 1.3.1 3.7.1s2.7 0 3.7-.1c.9 0 1.5-.2 2-.4a3.3 3.3 0 0 0 1.2-.8c.4-.4.6-.7.8-1.2.2-.5.4-1 .4-2 .1-1 .1-1.3.1-3.9s0-2.9-.1-3.9c0-.9-.2-1.5-.4-2a3.3 3.3 0 0 0-.8-1.2 3.3 3.3 0 0 0-1.2-.8c-.5-.2-1-.4-2-.4-1-.1-1.3-.1-3.7-.1Z"/></svg>
          </a>
        <% } %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2 class="footer-title">Snarvegar</h2>
      <ul class="footer-list footer-links">
        <li><a href="/kurs">Kurskalender</a></li>
        <li><a href="/pamelding">Påmelding til opplæring</a></li>
        <li><a href="/prisar">Prisar</a></li>
        <li><a href="/kjoretoy">Skulebilane våre</a></li>
        <li><a href="/gavekort">Gåvekort</a></li>
        <li><a href="/personvern">Personvern og informasjonskapslar</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="wrap footer-bottom">
    <p>© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= settings.siteName %> · <%= settings.tagline %></p>
    <p class="muted">I samarbeid med Storfjord Trafikk avd. Stranda/Sykkylven</p>
  </div>
</footer>

<div class="mobile-bar" aria-label="Snøggval">
  <a href="tel:+47<%= String(settings.locations[0].phone).replace(/\s/g,'') %>">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path fill="currentColor" d="M6.6 10.8a15.6 15.6 0 0 0 6.6 6.6l2.2-2.2c.3-.3.7-.4 1-.2 1.2.4 2.4.6 3.7.6.6 0 1 .4 1 1V20c0 .6-.4 1-1 1A17 17 0 0 1 3 4c0-.6.5-1 1-1h3.4c.6 0 1 .4 1 1 0 1.3.2 2.5.6 3.7.1.3 0 .7-.2 1Z"/></svg>
    Ring oss
  </a>
  <a href="/kurs">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19 4h-1V2h-2v2H8V2H6v2H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V6a2 2 0 0 0-2-2Zm0 16H5V10h14ZM5 8V6h14v2Z"/></svg>
    Kurs
  </a>
  <a href="/pamelding" class="mobile-bar-primary">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path fill="currentColor" d="M12 2 4 5v6c0 5 3.4 9.7 8 11 4.6-1.3 8-6 8-11V5Zm-1.2 13.5-3.3-3.3 1.4-1.4 1.9 1.9 4.3-4.3 1.4 1.4Z"/></svg>
    Meld deg på
  </a>
</div>

<div class="cookie-banner" id="cookieBanner" role="dialog" aria-live="polite" aria-label="Informasjonskapslar" hidden>
  <p>Vi brukar berre nødvendige informasjonskapslar for at sida skal fungere. Godtek du i tillegg tredjeparts-innhald (t.d. kart frå Google), kan du velje «Godta alle». Les meir i <a href="/personvern">personvernerklæringa</a>.</p>
  <div class="cookie-actions">
    <button class="btn btn-ghost" data-consent="necessary">Berre nødvendige</button>
    <button class="btn btn-primary" data-consent="all">Godta alle</button>
  </div>
</div>

<script src="/js/site.js?v=<%= locals.assetV %>" defer></script>
</body>
</html>
